comments: Hield (SAC) extends his arm toward Reddish's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs to Reddish's front as he moves around the screen.
Gallinari (ATL) firms up in his screening position in Hield's (SAC) path and absorbs the contact.
Barnes (SAC) briefly has his left arm around Okongwu's (ATL) midsection before quickly removing it.
Jones (SAC) brings his right forearm toward Reddish's (ATL) front and marginal contact occurs as Reddish is passing.
Hield (SAC) moves underneath Okongwu (ATL) during the dunk attempt and initiates body contact that affects Okongwu's ability to safely return to the floor.
Fox (SAC) goes to, not through, Wright's (ATL) space as marginal contact occurs at the end of Fox's drive.

Gallinari's (ATL) right forearm is rested on Jones' (SAC) back and marginal contact occurs as Jones jumps toward the rim during rebounding. Gallinari and Jones then each raise their right arms and incidental contact occurs as the rebound falls.
Replay review of the out of bounds call on SAC pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Gallinari's (ATL) right hand touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Hield (SAC) and Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL) engage and disengage with one another in the lane during the inbound.
Wright (ATL) and Haliburton (SAC) engage and disengage with one another off ball.

Reddish (ATL) legally contests Haliburton's (SAC) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental. After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor of a three point basket was confirmed.
Capela (ATL) turns to begin rolling toward the lane and incidental body contact occurs with Hield (SAC) as Hield goes over the pick.
Wright (ATL) moves toward Hield's (SAC) path and marginal body contact occurs as Wright drives into the lane.
Harkless (SAC) legally contests Reddish's (ATL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Huerter (ATL) briefly has his hands around Haliburton's (SAC) upper half before correcting.
Capela (ATL) jumps from point A to point B and delivers body contact to Fox (SAC) during the driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) engages and disengages with Jones (SAC) in the lane.
Mitchell (SAC) moves somewhat laterally toward Huerter (ATL) and marginal body contact occurs prior to Huerter's gather.
Mitchell (SAC) is retreating alongside Huerter's (ATL) path and is bringing his arm into a vertical position as he absorbs the contact during Huerter's driving shot attempt.
Wright (ATL) swipes down and initiates contact with Fox's (SAC) left elbow during his upward shooting motion.
Fox (SAC) commits a take foul on Huerter (ATL).
Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Wright's (ATL) path and absorbs the contact.
Hield (SAC) engages and disengages with Wright (ATL) as they move over the screen.
Jones (SAC) establishes himself in a screening position in Wright's (ATL) path and does not deliver the contact as Wright goes under.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Hield (SAC) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Harkless (SAC) grasps and then quickly releases Huerter's (ATL) jersey during the inbound.
Williams (ATL) engages and disengages with Mitchell (SAC) during the inbound.
Harkless (SAC) commits a take foul on Huerter (ATL).
Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL) extends into Fox's (SAC) path and initiates body contact that affects Fox's SQBR.
Fox (SAC) and Luwawu-Cabarrot (ATL) each make clean contact with the ball and the ball becomes dislodged prior to any incidental arm contact occurring.
Harkless (SAC) and Capela (ATL) engage on the long rebound on the other side of the floor..
Gallinari (ATL) and Barnes (SAC) make incidental contact with one another as they each pursue the loose ball in the corner.
Hield (SAC) commits a take foul on Gallinari (ATL).
